evidence: Using X-ray measurements, you perform a physical or mathematical transform from f of x, y to p of theta, t.

triples.evidence: If you have a parallel beam at projection angle theta, and you have, say, one hundred rays or five hundred rays, then you have one hundred or five hundred linear system equations.
